kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c5f2bef32ec6e08ec2ea54f44b2ac7f9d4aa07","tid":1589173,"uid":179649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"又話8月4到6號岀解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到開心左幾日<br />\nOn99  <br />\n張學友話齋 : 喫屎啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f9e628be9344f81b0f369edb690b6a5a924a64","tid":1589173,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"又燈？"},{"pid":"07e8787ca12766b782049338b579f6ba5efb043e","tid":1589173,"uid":34935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"係出摺被師就快啦<br />\n好撚期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18c120da52c7ceb4b88e63a09179f99e6eaccaf","tid":1589173,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"范冰冰呢"},{"pid":"720f8008ef3f95c4c1a0927ec6cd803fdc5f2eaf","tid":1589173,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：2020年中共仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK64%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=f4726d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98uJ9C2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98uJ9C2.png&h=4cc64ccf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾</strong></span></span>」。"},{"pid":"d92ec1bf028fdba4c00eed729b274ae129ef5ed8","tid":1589173,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720f8008ef3f95c4c1a0927ec6cd803fdc5f2eaf","tid":1589173,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：2020年中共仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK64%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=f4726d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98uJ9C2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98uJ9C2.png&h=4cc64ccf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾</strong></span></span>」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇個勢未到2020年西方各國已圍堵中國<br />\n<br />\n佢話會打柒香港寶島 我當佢冇鳩up先<br />\n<br />\n係中國國內一半人要返返去鄉下姦田 但d地神早賣曬 起曬樓 種條毛咩 就算有田 但已經污染曬<br />\n而中國人多 糧食儲備開始小 前排先有新聞講中共已經拎左 豬肉儲備出嚟頂住先 但頂得幾耐 口硬得幾耐<br />\n<br />\n我諗閘大條小學雞係諗住用對外戰嚟轉移視線穩住中共嘅江山 但佢冇諗過打輪左會有咩下場以為一定贏咁"},{"pid":"865a929031b46718edb5966ea2d6cf41f9f2ec36","tid":1589173,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"哦，哈"},{"pid":"c9b76f25d75e3b2d51a34371dcab6f0c6bb0b79f","tid":1589173,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:27:58.000Z","msg":"佢唔係逃亡咩<br />\n<br />\n走左咁多年 咩風都冇晒啦<br />\n<br />\n佢講到中共咁堅 &nbsp;邊個夠膽比料佢<br />\n<br />\n仲要起中國國境"},{"pid":"d3dbda2c72df4950bd45b29bf25f131ef9b5e428","tid":1589173,"uid":261415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"再吹大啲啦。范冰冰條片又唔找數。大陸武統台灣講左咁鳩耐都未打。係就快。"},{"pid":"905e89c4c3b3bc18799625066578e14d25c35ebd","tid":1589173,"uid":294182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"台灣啲國民黨老兵等咗解放軍一世都冇嚟過台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2353d6d6b96d02d2d78dc6b746066e06ff492598","tid":1589173,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"928 念雨革 929 驅共狗 101 賀牛一"}]}